ed seating. the deck is also used in cooler weather as well with their drop-down curtains to keep the elements out and they heaters to keep the temperature comfortable. stools also line this bar as well. cash or credit and you can always start a tab. i believe tuesdays they now have a bingo event available as well as a dart league. bartenders are always friendly and if you frequent enough remember your libation of choice. one of the best bars to go to in shadyside whether you are gay or straight.", "business_id": "7pgmsGEqV7yawGM4b4fRrw", "stars": 4, "date": "2012-07-10", "type": "review"}